import React, { Component } from 'react'
import './Checkbox.css'

class Checkbox extends Component {
    constructor(props){
        super(props)
    }

    render() {
        return (
            <section className="checkbox-selectItens">
                <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    name="hack"
                    id="hack"
                    value="hack"/>
                <label 
                    className="checkbox-selectItens"
                    htmlFor="hack">
                        Hack
                    </label>
                <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    name="estante"
                    id="estante"
                    value="estante"/>
                <label 
                    className="checkbox-selectItens"
                    htmlFor="estante">
                        Estante
                    </label>
                <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    name="televisao"
                    id="televisao"
                    value="televisao"/>
                <label 
                    className="checkbox-selectItens"
                    htmlFor="televisao">
                        Televis√£o
                    </label>
                <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    name="mesa4p"
                    id="mesa4p"
                    value="mesa4p"/>
                <label 
                    className="checkbox-selectItens"
                    htmlFor="mesa4p">
                        Mesa para 4 pessoas
                    </label>
                <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    name="3cadeiras"
                    id="3cadeiras"
                    value="3cadeiras"/>
                <label 
                    className="checkbox-selectItens"
                    htmlFor="3cadeiras">
                        3 cadeiras
                    </label>
            </section>
        )
    }
}

export default Checkbox
